<script type="text/javascript">
	var doUpdate = function(){
		//Header menu mouse over
		var hover_flg = false;

		if(hover_flg == false){
			$('.HeadCartView.hoverMenu, .scroll-nav .liCartList').mouseenter(function(){
				$(this).find('.menu').stop(false, false).fadeIn(500, function(){
					hover_flg = true;
				});
			});
		}

			$('.HeadCartView.hoverMenu, .scroll-nav .liCartList').mouseleave(function(){
				if(hover_flg == true){
					$(this).find('.menu').stop(false, false).fadeOut(500, function(){
						hover_flg = false;
					});
				}
			});

		$(".closePopUpCartList, .popupCartList").click(function () {
			$("div.popupCartList").fadeOut();
		})
	};

	function ShowPopupCartList() {
		$("div.popupCartList").fadeIn();
	}

	if (Sys && Sys.Application) {
		Sys.Application.add_load(doUpdate);
	}
	else {
		doUpdate();
	}

	var h_search_timer;

	$('.h-search input').focusin(function(e) {
		$('.h-search').addClass('show');
	})
	.focusout(function(e) {
		$('.h-search').removeClass('show');
	});

	$('.pc_btn_menu_wrap').bind('mouseenter', function(){

		if(!$(this).hasClass('show')){

			$(this).addClass('show');
			$('.pc_menu_wrap').stop(false, false).fadeIn();

		}else{

			$('.pc_menu_wrap').stop(false, false).fadeOut();
			$('.pc_btn_menu_wrap').removeClass('show');

		}
	});

	$('.pc_btn_menu_wrap').bind('mouseleave', function(){
		h_search_timer = setTimeout(function(){
			trace("common");
			$('.pc_menu_wrap').stop(false, false).fadeOut();
			$('.pc_btn_menu_wrap.show').removeClass('show');
		},400)
	});



	$('.pc_btn_menu_wrap').bind('click', function(){

		if(!$(this).hasClass('show')){
			$(this).addClass('show');
			$('.pc_menu_wrap').stop(false, false).fadeIn();
		}else{
			$('.pc_menu_wrap').stop(false, false).fadeOut();
			$('.pc_btn_menu_wrap.show').removeClass('show');
		}
	});

	$('.pc_menu_wrap').bind('mouseleave', function(){
		clearTimeout(h_search_timer);

		}else{
			$('.pc_menu_wrap').stop(false, false).fadeOut();

		}
	});
	$('.pc_menu_wrap').bind('mousemove', function(){

});

<script>
// 送料無料バナー jsonp読み込み
function pcShippingFree(){
    var $tbsp_elm = $(".brn_members.show_pc.mb5");
    var this_location = location.href;
    var STAGE_URL = '/Test/084_RightOn/';
    var this_local_url = '/';
    var JSON_PATH = 'https://right-on.co.jp/api/banner_t5.php?callback=myfunc';

    if(this_location.indexOf(STAGE_URL) != -1){
      this_local_url = STAGE_URL;
      JSON_PATH = "https://right-on.co.jp/debugapi/jsonp_debug.php?t=5&callback=myfunc";
    }

    var json_obj_arr = [];
    var json_obj = {}; /*json data obj*/
    json_obj.table = ["id","type","category","category_name","status","disp_order","title","label","title_sp","label_sp","link_url","link_target","image_src_pc","image_src_thum","image_src_sp","start_datetime","stop_datetime","disabled","category_num"];
    var json_len;

    var html_li_str = "";
    var pc_html_li_str = "";
    var img_count_num = {};
    img_count_num.main_pic = 0;
    img_count_num.main_pic_sp = 0;


    init();
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // 初期化
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    function init(){
        loadJsonp();
    }

    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // jsonp 読み込み
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    function loadJsonp() {
        $.ajax({
          type: 'GET',
          url:JSON_PATH+"?Math.random()",
          dataType: 'jsonp',
          timeout: 10000,
          success:onLoadedJson,
          error:onErrorLoadJson
        });
    }

    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // json読み込み完了
    // 配列にデータ格納
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    function onLoadedJson(_data){
        var json = _data;
        json_len = json.length;
        for(var i = 0; i < json_len; i++){
            var temp_arr = [];

            for(var j = 0; j < json_obj.table.length; j++){
                temp_arr[json_obj.table[j]] = json[i][json_obj.table[j]];
            }
            json_obj_arr[i] = temp_arr;
        }
        htmlSet();
    }

    function onErrorLoadJson(_XMLHttpsRequest, _textStatus, _errorThrown){
    trace("XMLHttpRequest : " + XMLHttpRequest.status + "\n" + "textStatus : " + _textStatus + "\n" + "errorThrown : " + _errorThrown.message);
  }

    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // html append
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    function htmlSet(){
        for(var i = 0; i < json_len; i++){
            $tbsp_elm.append(PChtmlLi(i));
        }
    }

    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // li html生成
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
     function PChtmlLi(_i){
        var loadImage = new Image();
        var this_json_url = json_obj_arr[_i].link_url;

        if(this_json_url.indexOf('http') != -1){
          this_local_url = '';
        }else{
          if(this_location.indexOf('/SmartPhone/') != -1){
            if(this_location.indexOf(STAGE_URL) != -1){
              this_local_url = STAGE_URL;
            }else{
              this_local_url = '/';
            }
          }
        }

        loadImage.src = json_obj_arr[_i].image_src_pc;
        pc_html_li_str = '';
        pc_html_li_str += '<a href="'+this_local_url+json_obj_arr[_i].link_url+'" target="'+json_obj_arr[_i].link_target+'">';
        pc_html_li_str += '<img src="'+json_obj_arr[_i].image_src_pc+'" alt="" width="203">';
        pc_html_li_str += '</a>';

        loadImage.onload = function(){
            img_count_num.main_pic++;
        }
        return pc_html_li_str;
    }
}


$(function(){
  pcShippingFree();
});
</script>

	// Focus to color when display
	$( document ).ready( function ()
	{
		// Focus color after search
		var colorValue = "";
		if ( colorValue != "" )
		{
			var itemColor = document.getElementById( colorValue );
			FocusColor( itemColor );
		}
		colorCheckboxCheck();
		hoverColorText();
    sizeListCheck();
		$('#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox1_cblSizeSearch input').bind('click', function(){
			colorCheckboxCheck();
		});
	} );

	// Choose color
	function SetColor( itemColor )
  {
    var colorSelect = $( "#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox1_hfColorSelect" ).val();

    // Choose color
    if ( $( itemColor ).attr( "id" ) != colorSelect )
    {
      var currentColor = document.getElementById( colorSelect );
      $( currentColor ).css( "border-color", "#f4f6f7" );
      $( "#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox1_hfColorSelect" ).val( "" );
      FocusColor( itemColor );
    }

    // Cancel choose color
    if ( $( itemColor ).attr( "id" ) == colorSelect )
    {
      $( "#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox1_hfColorSelect" ).val( "" );
      $( itemColor ).removeClass('act');
    }
  }

	function FocusColor( itemColor )
	{
		$( '.js_select_btn' ).removeClass('act');
		$( "#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox1_hfColorSelect" ).val( $( itemColor ).attr( "id" ) );
		$( itemColor ).addClass('act');
	}

	function colorCheckboxCheck(){
		$('#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox1_cblSizeSearch td').removeClass('act');
		$('#cat_800 input:checked').each(function(_i){
			$(this).parents('td').addClass('act');
		});
	}

	function hoverColorText(){
		$('.js_select_btn').each(function(_i){
			$(this).append('<span class="hide_hover">'+ $(this).find('span').attr('title') +'</span>');
		});
		$('.js_select_btn').bind('mouseenter', function(){
			$(this).find('.hide_hover').show();
		});
		$('.js_select_btn').bind('mouseleave', function(){
			$(this).find('.hide_hover').hide();
		});
	}

  function sizeListCheck(){
    var html = $('#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox1_sizeBox ul.cat2nd.size_list li').text();
    if(html.length == 0){
      $('#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox1_sizeBox').remove();
    }
  }

</script>

<script>
// 送料無料バナー jsonp読み込み
function sptbShippingFree(){
    var $tbsp_elm = $(".brn_members.show_tbsp.mb10");
    var this_location = location.href;
    var STAGE_URL = '/Test/084_RightOn/';
    var this_local_url = '/';
    var JSON_PATH = 'https://right-on.co.jp/api/banner_t3.php?callback=myfunc';

    if(this_location.indexOf(STAGE_URL) != -1){
      this_local_url = STAGE_URL;
      JSON_PATH = "https://right-on.co.jp/debugapi/jsonp_debug.php?t=3&callback=myfunc";
    }

    var json_obj_arr = [];
    var json_obj = {}; /*json data obj*/
    json_obj.table = ["id","type","category","category_name","status","disp_order","title","label","title_sp","label_sp","link_url","link_target","image_src_pc","image_src_thum","image_src_sp","start_datetime","stop_datetime","disabled","category_num"];
    var json_len;

    var html_li_str = "";
    var sptb_html_li_str = "";
    var img_count_num = {};
    img_count_num.main_pic = 0;
    img_count_num.main_pic_sp = 0;


    init();
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // 初期化
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    function init(){
        loadJsonp();
    }

    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // jsonp 読み込み
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    function loadJsonp() {
        $.ajax({
          type: 'GET',
          url:JSON_PATH+"?Math.random()",
          dataType: 'jsonp',
          timeout: 10000,
          success:onLoadedJson,
          error:onErrorLoadJson
        });
    }

    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // json読み込み完了
    // 配列にデータ格納
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    function onLoadedJson(_data){
        var json = _data;
        json_len = json.length;
        for(var i = 0; i < json_len; i++){
            var temp_arr = [];

            for(var j = 0; j < json_obj.table.length; j++){
                temp_arr[json_obj.table[j]] = json[i][json_obj.table[j]];
            }
            json_obj_arr[i] = temp_arr;
        }
        htmlSet();
    }

    function onErrorLoadJson(_XMLHttpRequest, _textStatus, _errorThrown){
    trace("XMLHttpRequest : " + XMLHttpRequest.status + "\n" + "textStatus : " + _textStatus + "\n" + "errorThrown : " + _errorThrown.message);
  }

    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // html append
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    function htmlSet(){
        for(var i = 0; i < json_len; i++){
            $tbsp_elm.append(SPTBhtmlLi(i));
        }
    }

    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
    // li html生成
    //----------------------------------------------------------------------
     function SPTBhtmlLi(_i){
        var loadImage = new Image();
        var loadImage2 = new Image();
        var this_json_url = json_obj_arr[_i].link_url;

        if(this_json_url.indexOf('http') != -1){
          this_local_url = '';
        }else{
          if(this_location.indexOf('/SmartPhone/') != -1){
            if(this_location.indexOf(STAGE_URL) != -1){
              this_local_url = STAGE_URL;
            }else{
              this_local_url = '/';
            }
          }
        }

        loadImage2.src = json_obj_arr[_i].image_src_sp;
        loadImage.src = json_obj_arr[_i].image_src_pc;
        sptb_html_li_str = '';
        sptb_html_li_str += '<a href="'+this_local_url+json_obj_arr[_i].link_url+'" target="'+json_obj_arr[_i].link_target+'">';
        sptb_html_li_str += '<img src="'+json_obj_arr[_i].image_src_sp+'" alt="" width="100%" class="show_sp">';
        sptb_html_li_str += '<img src="'+json_obj_arr[_i].image_src_pc+'" alt="" width="100%" class="show_tb">';
        sptb_html_li_str += '</a>';
        loadImage2.onload = function(){
            img_count_num.main_pic_sp++;
        }
        loadImage.onload = function(){
            img_count_num.main_pic++;
        }
        return sptb_html_li_str;
    }
}


$(function(){
  sptbShippingFree();
});
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">

	// Focus to color when display
	$( document ).ready( function ()
	{
		// Focus color after search
		var colorValue = "";
		if ( colorValue != "" )
		{
			var itemColor = document.getElementById( "sp_" + colorValue );
			$( itemColor ).addClass( "selected" );
			FocusColorSp( itemColor );
		}
	} );

	// Choose color
	function SetColorSp( itemColor )
	{
		var colorSelect = $( "#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox2_hfColorSelect" ).val();

		trace("colorSelect:"+colorSelect);

		// Choose color
		if ( $( itemColor ).attr( "id" ) != ( "sp_" + colorSelect ) )
		{
			var currentColor = document.getElementById( "sp_" + colorSelect );
			// 現在、選択されている項目をキャンセル
			$( currentColor ).css( "border-color", "#f4f6f7" );
			$( currentColor ).removeClass( "selected" );

			$( "#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox2_hfColorSelect" ).val( "" );
			$( itemColor ).addClass( "selected" );
			FocusColorSp( itemColor );
		}

		if ( $( itemColor ).attr( "id" ) == ( "sp_" + colorSelect ) )
		{
			// Cancel choose color
			$( ".selectColor.selected" ).first().removeClass( "selected" );

			$( "#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox2_hfColorSelect" ).val( "" );
			$( itemColor ).css( "border-color", "#f4f6f7" );
			$( itemColor ).removeClass( "selected" );
		}
	}

	function FocusColorSp( itemColor )
	{
		$( "#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox2_hfColorSelect" ).val( $( itemColor ).attr( "id" ).replace( "sp_", "" ) );
		// $( "#ctl00_ContentPlaceHolder1_ColorSizeSearchBox2_hfColorSelect" ).val( $( itemColor ).attr( "id" ) );
	}
</script>
